& [LiveShaliachSelfNegotiationBoundaryDesign] is the design boundary for live-model Shaliach internal negotiation
  @ [created_at] 2026-05-30T17:12:00Z
  @ [triggering_slice] S294_live_shaliach_self_negotiation_boundary_design
  @ [related_spec] specifications/Hierarchical_Agent_Swarm.sop
  @ [related_code] src/negotiated_agent/shaliach.py
  @ [related_code] src/negotiated_agent/llm.py
  @ [related_probe] coordination/openai_health.sop
  @ [related_route] coordination/live_route_config_draft.sop

  + [problem] is Shaliach self-negotiation is currently deterministic scaffold evidence rather than live model-negotiated counsel
  + [problem] is local serving remains unavailable so live Shaliach integration must not block dry-run proof or pretend live deliberation occurred
  + [decision] is add live-ready Shaliach self-negotiation as an optional overlay on top of deterministic scaffold records
  + [decision] is deterministic ShaliachSelfNegotiationRecord remains the required baseline artifact for every layer
  + [decision] is live Shaliach perspective records may be added only when endpoint health is available and route config names a Shaliach provider/model
  + [decision] is live failures degrade to deterministic scaffold status with explicit live_status blocked_or_unavailable
  + [authority_boundary] is live_ready_boundary_not_live_deliberation_proof

& [LiveInputPacket] is the minimum prompt evidence for live Shaliach internal negotiation
  + [input] is subject_ref
  + [input] is context_boundary
  + [input] is ShaliachFinding fields and severity/action/confidence
  + [input] is deterministic perspective_set and proposed_response_set
  + [input] is protocol activation refs where available
  + [input] is combined validation or checkpoint proof ref when the subject is a continuation decision
  + [non_input] is raw hidden chain-of-thought
  + [authority_boundary] is prompt_packet_not_private_reasoning_dump

& [LiveOutputBoundary] is the required shape of live Shaliach responses
  + [output] is live_status available, unavailable, failed, or skipped_by_policy
  + [output] is model_ref
  + [output] is perspective_response legal_counsel
  + [output] is perspective_response protocol_officer
  + [output] is perspective_response failure_advocate
  + [output] is perspective_response purpose_guardian
  + [output] is resolved_intention_delta
  + [output] is unresolved_tension_set
  + [output] is authority_boundary live_shaliach_review_not_manager_approval
  + [non_output] is final code acceptance

& [FallbackPolicy] is the blocked-safe behavior while local serving is unavailable
  + [condition] is OpenAI-compatible health unavailable or Ollama unavailable
  + [behavior] is emit deterministic ShaliachSelfNegotiationRecord exactly as today
  + [behavior] is optionally emit LiveShaliachSelfNegotiationAttempt with live_status unavailable
  + [behavior] is do not change ShaliachFinding severity based on missing live serving
  + [behavior] is keep long-run checkpoint ready_for_continuation when all deterministic proof gates pass
  + [authority_boundary] is missing_live_serving_not_protocol_failure

& [ImplementationPlan] is the next staged build path
  + [slice_1] is add LiveShaliachSelfNegotiationAttempt record type and parser with unavailable/failed/available statuses
  + [slice_2] is add pure prompt packet builder from ShaliachSelfNegotiationRecord and ShaliachFinding fields
  + [slice_3] is add CLI preview that writes unavailable attempt when endpoint health is not available
  + [slice_4] is add optional orchestrator hook gated by config and endpoint health
  + [slice_5] is later replace deterministic perspective responses with live model responses only when local serving is verified

& [AcceptanceCriteria] is the proof required before claiming live Shaliach readiness
  + [criterion] is tests prove unavailable endpoint writes unavailable attempt and preserves deterministic self-negotiation record
  + [criterion] is tests prove live-ready prompt packet excludes hidden reasoning and includes protocol/proof refs
  + [criterion] is tests prove live attempt status cannot be confused with Manager approval or Shaliach clearance
  + [criterion] is live health unavailable remains non-gating for deterministic long-run checkpoint proof
